How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

  • Some couple who buys things
    5.0 out of 5 stars Bright
    Reviewed in the United States on October 26, 2024
    Color: Purple GreenAmazon Vine Customer Review of Free Product( What's this? )
    These small action figures have been the greatest gifts I could give out to all the children in my life. Boys and girls both love them. They are cheap and well worth the wait.

    The pieces pop together and apart just like lego or knex. They stay together well and provide hours of fun. Most of them are interchangeable and can make many brightly colored designs. The little weapons they come with only add to this. Despite being 3d printed they are more solid than most store bought toys.

    Though they are small they have a rather large impact. I will continue to gather more of them throughout the years because they are also good collector toys.
